			<div class="content" id="post-content-1120851">
									

<p>I wasn't clear - I don't think you need a picture of THEM, just a picture of SOMETHING. That's a bit longer then the average article. A picture would have prevented me from thinking "tl;dr" the first time I saw it, and instead think "How is THAT related to… What is this again?"</p>
<p>As for SCP-914:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>WARNING: At this time, no testing of biological matter is allowed. Refer to document 109-B:117.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>There's, like, three references to it. Besides, aside from the REDACTED section, there was nothing that wasn't fixed by a mop. (Honestly, you'd have to find a pathologically insane O5 to authorize Very Fine on something like THAT!)</p>

